@startuml
title Math Values - Level 1

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

package "Values used everywhere" {
	class Vector2
	class Rect2D
	class Color
	class Duration
}

package "Widgets" {
	class Widget
}

package "Rendering" {
	class RenderCommand
	class Mesh
	class Image
}

Widget --> Rect2D : position and size
Widget --> Vector2 : points and movement
Widget --> Duration : update time
RenderCommand --> Color : tint or fill
Mesh --> Vector2 : vertices
Image --> Rect2D : source area

note bottom
Sparkle's small value types keep geometry, color,
and time explicit instead of passing raw numbers around.
end note

@enduml
